This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with the detection of pulmonary nodules in CT scans using deep learning methods. It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories as it involves the development of a novel deep convolutional neural network for nodule detection. Additionally, it may belong to the Medical Imaging (cs.MS) and Multimedia (cs.MM) categories as it deals with the analysis of medical images and the use of deep learning for image processing.
